    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. The Test conditions factor achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3; however, the team judges this shortfall acceptable given that the single ASTM F1717 condition is the regulatory standard condition and the E/uval metric is satisfied for all QoIs. Overall credibility is assessed as Medium, consistent with the model risk level of 3 and medium model influence and decision consequence. The package is accepted for submission.",
